-- Pound Rebounds After U.S. Report Shows Payrolls Drop More Than Estimated
-- Keith Campbell
-- 2010-08-06T12:34:35Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-08-06/pound-rebounds-after-u-s-report-shows-payrolls-drop-more-than-estimated.html

          
          
             The pound erased its decline against
the dollar after the U.S. shed more jobs than economists had
estimated. Sterling was up less than 0.1 percent to $1.5904 at
1:33 p.m. in London after earlier losing as much as 0.4 percent.  
          
          


  


        